    <h2>Selected Work</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <a href="https://venice.fibn.cc/">Venice</a> - an open-source alternative
            to VEXcode Python.
            <br />
            <strong>Role:</strong> main developer; wrote MicroPython bindings, V5
            system HAL and CLI tool.
        </li>
        <li>
            <a href="https://github.com/fibonacci61/yaro">Yaro</a> - a toy RISC-V
